    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Reaping tools with L-shaped wooden handles and a blade. Siths allowed the user to stand upright, holding the crop with the mathook in the left hand, and cutting the crop with the sith in the right, which was different than with scythes.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
